http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/karnataka/Catch-the-best-films-here/article14022588.ece

Get ready to witness a sea of films this month-end as the 8th edition of BIFFes has scheduled over 140 films for screening in Mysuru and 170 films in Bengaluru.The films will be screened under the following categories — Asian Cinema, Biopic, Cinema of the World, Climate Change and Drought, Country Focus, Grand Classics, Homage, Indian Cinema Competition–Chitrabharathi, Indian Currents, International Currents, Kannada Cinema, Kannada Dialect, Netpac, Recommended Screening, Retrospectives, Special Theme and WorldPremiere.